<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨٦٧ -<span class="c5"> ومنها:</span> قَالَ لِي <span class="c2">((نَاوِلِينِي الْخُمْرَةَ مِنَ الْمَسْجِدِ)</span>) فَقُلْتُ: إِنِّي حَائِضٌ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">((إِنَّ حَيْضَتَكِ لَيْسَتْ فِي يَدِكِ)</span>) <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
